Spring is a great time to rid your home of winter clutter and spruce things up a bit. But with everyone looking for ways to save money these days, it can be tough to find cheap and easy ways to redecorate and redesign. That's why we've put together these 46 thrifty ideas for decorating on a budget. You'll find
DIY decor ideas for every room of the house, including the kitchen, living room, bathroom and kids room. We even have a great selection of wall art ideas that you can hang just about anywhere.
